{"tid":1661284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗日報因資金緊絀已暫停所有直播,急需大家幫忙  ↠↠ 冇錢都可以幫到 ↞↞","createTime":"2019-10-18T04:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T05:01:00.000Z","uid":315185,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1440093e1df309b1d1fa3d3e85e2f33afb1ece","tid":1661284,"uid":315185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RgqZnCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRgqZnCQ.jpg&h=7418d78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>睇節目已經話資源緊拙 Facebook仲話暫停所有直播</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><strong>主要方法:課金</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">訂閱癲狗日報 月費:$200</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">可經Paypal/銀行户口/親臨癲狗日報辦公室繳費<br />\n方法及收費表如下:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/md-pricelist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fmd-pricelist%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=a0b2e65f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/md-pricelist/</a><br />\n&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;<br />\n因為癲狗日報係<span style=\"color: violet;\">急需</span>資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有能力 直接課金應該最快最直接<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>次要方法:到youtube睇廣告</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇廣告 唔好略過<br />\n唔好開阻截廣告插件</span></span><br />\n<strong>MyRadio Hong Kong</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSJ7F-9d351iCvla2IzAQoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCSJ7F-9d351iCvla2IzAQoQ&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=5f73b971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSJ7F-9d351iCvla2IzAQoQ</a><br />\n以及 <strong>黃毓民頻道</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/yukmanofficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fyukmanofficial&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=cb4302e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/yukmanofficial</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>***可以順便聽下黃毓民鬧人 有時心情會好返啲</em></span><br />\n<br />\n其實癲狗日報好多時都好快有直播<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>有啲片段都係癲狗日報影到而且記者都有受傷</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>&quot; 8月4 癲狗日報記者於黃大仙被防暴警以警棍扑暈&quot;<br />\n&quot; 9月6 油尖旺男子持刀追斬癲狗日報記者&quot;<br />\n&quot; 9月29 癲狗日報記者於鵝頸橋街市被的士惡意撞擊&quot;</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>希望大家幫幫癲狗日報</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">多個記者 有咩事可能多段片幫到手足</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9777f7e9f0788d8680a344b79a684a67e37f7777","tid":1661284,"uid":200665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b377464c8d01075b987568b8ca9a543a32a8fb44","tid":1661284,"uid":498,"like":11,"dislike":25,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T04:19:06.000Z","msg":"黃匪垃圾台終於收皮<br />\n唔撚使再有呢類廢物污染空氣<br />\n佢同港人港地同lv 賤"},{"pid":"46cab62a920e022db15f897a2a48c00a6fb47f26","tid":1661284,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco